-- China Calls for Preparation for Tropical Storm, Xinhua Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-06-28T16:53:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/china-calls-for-preparation-for-tropical-storm-xinhua-reports.html
Chinese authorities called for civil
affairs departments in four coastal provinces to prepare for
approaching Tropical Storm Doksuri, Xinhua News Agency reported,
citing the State Disaster Relief Commission.  The provinces of Fujian, Guangdong, Guangxi and Hainan were
asked to quickly issue early-warning information, Xinhua
reported.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
